  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Knowledge sharing on macroeconomic policy to promote full and productive employment</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main project outcome is &#x201C;policy makers and technical experts appreciate the linkages between employment-friendly macroeconomic policies, structural reforms and sectoral policies to develop employment-friendly macroeconomic policies to achieve the goal of full and productive and decent employment for all&#x201D;. The project aims to organize and support a knowledge-sharing and dissemination forum for research outputs on macroeocnomic policy framework and employment, produced by GLO/09/50/ROK and GLO/10/53/ROK + those supported by regular budgetary sources.</narrative>
  </description>
